OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Correspondent Peter
OL,7,FSmith and Deputy Content Editor Greg
OL,8,FOckrim
OL,10,FElections are often remembered for the
OL,11,Fbig moments. In what has been a fairly
OL,12,Funeventful Scottish election so far,
OL,13,FTuesday night had what felt like the
OL,14,Ffirst pivotal moment.
OL,16,FAmid political mudslinging during a
OL,17,Ftelevised Channel 4 debate between all
OL,18,Fof the Scottish party leaders, a
OL,19,Fseries of allegations were made.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
