OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776287489
OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FFirst, by Scottish Labour's Anas
OL,7,FSarwar, that Reform UK were fielding
OL,8,Fcandidates who wanted to deport
OL,9,FMuslims even if they were born in the
OL,10,FUK.
OL,12,FIt got personal.
OL,14,F"One of his candidates wants to deport
OL,15,Fmy children," Sarwar said, pointing
OL,16,Fhis finger at Reform's leader in
OL,17,FScotland, Malcolm Offord.
OL,19,F"Where do you want them to go,
OL,20,FMalcolm?"
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@MO]{D@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
