OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThen the counter came.
OL,13,FOfford alleged that Sarwar had
OL,14,Fpreviously approached him, trying to
OL,15,Fstrike a deal between their parties to
OL,16,Foust the SNP.
OL,18,FHe said the approach was made last
OL,19,Fyear, and that Sarwar had told him
OL,20,Fthey must work together - something
OL,21,Fthat Sarwar immediately denied.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
