OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FThe accusation that Labour has been
OL,7,Ftrying to "work with" Reform has
OL,8,Fimmediately been pounced upon by the
OL,9,FSNP, with the heated moment from the
OL,10,Fdebate widely shared on their social
OL,11,Fmedia accounts.
OL,13,FThe fallout continued on Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith Malcom Offord standing by his
OL,15,Fallegation, and other members of
OL,16,FReform claiming to either have
OL,17,Fwitnessed or experienced similar
OL,18,Fconversations with Anas Sarwar.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
