OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776287489
OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FMalcolm Offord insists Anas Sarwar did
OL,7,Fsuggest Scottish Labour and Reform UK
OL,8,Fshould work together to keep the SNP
OL,9,Fout of power
OL,11,FOne Reform candidate went into detail,
OL,12,Fsaying Sarwar had proposed that their
OL,13,Frespective parties should "shadow box
OL,14,Funtil the election".
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, the Scottish Labour
OL,17,Fleader categorically denied all of
OL,18,Fthis, calling it "lies".
OL,26,@uD@[OUvD@SO]zD@ROUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
