OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FITV News put it to Sarwar that Reform
OL,7,Fnow claim to have witnesses, and
OL,8,Fallege the proposal to do a deal
OL,9,Fhappened on more than one occasion.
OL,11,FAgain, the Scottish Labour leader
OL,12,Fdenied this, saying it was "nonsense."
OL,14,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,15,Fdenied that he said the party would do
OL,16,Fa deal with Reform UK
OL,26,@tD@\OUtD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
