OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776287489
OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FIf leaders of the other main parties
OL,7,Fwere hoping to be talking about their
OL,8,Fown policies on scheduled campaign
OL,9,Fvisits this morning, they instead
OL,10,Ffound themselves reacting to the
OL,11,Falleged proposal turned spat.
OL,13,FAnd in some cases, distancing
OL,14,Fthemselves from the prospect of ever
OL,15,Fworking with Nigel Farage's Scotland
OL,16,Fbranch of the Reform Party.
OL,18,FDuring a visit to South Ayrshire, the
OL,19,FSNP leader John Swinney said: "What's
OL,20,Fimportant is Labour and Reform explain
OL,21,Fthemselves.
OL,26,@{D@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
