OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776287489
OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,F"For me, I'll set out to people in
OL,7,FScotland that I'll have nothing to do
OL,8,Fwith Reform whatsoever."
OL,10,FScottish Greens co-leader Gillian
OL,11,FMackay said her party would "never do
OL,12,Fany kind of deal with Reform", as she
OL,13,Fcalled on other parties to make the
OL,14,Fsame commitment.
OL,16,F"Any government that relied on Reform
OL,17,Fto get into power would be a disaster
OL,18,Ffor Scotland.
OL,26,@sD@]OUtD@]O]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
