OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,F"Labour supporters across the country
OL,7,Fwould be shocked if they did any deals
OL,8,Fwith a party like Reform or relied on
OL,9,Fthe votes of Reform MSPs to take
OL,10,Fpower," she said.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Conservative leader,
OL,13,FRussell Findlay, was at the event
OL,14,Fwhere Offord alleges Sarwar made an
OL,15,Fapproach.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
