OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FHe said: "I think this is the usual
OL,7,Fpolitical bubble nonsense. Last night,
OL,8,Fwhile Anas Sarwar and Lord Offord were
OL,9,Fconducting this phoney argument over
OL,10,Fwho said what, when. It turns people
OL,11,Foff, it's boring."
OL,13,FAlex Cole-Hamilton, the leader of the
OL,14,FScottish Liberal Democrats, said: "The
OL,15,FLiberal Democrats won't have anything
OL,16,Fto do with reform in the next
OL,17,Fparliament, and I don't believe Labour
OL,18,Fwill do either. I think it's dirty
OL,19,Ftricks by Lord Offord."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
