OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FIn front of the cameras, the
OL,7,Frelationship between the two appears
OL,8,Fto be personal. Sarwar has accused
OL,9,FReform of racism and called Lord
OL,10,FOfford a "vile" and "odious little
OL,11,Fman" who is "toxic" to Scottish
OL,12,Fpolitics.
OL,14,FThis began over the Reform Party's
OL,15,Fbillboard adverts, which showed a
OL,16,Fsmall boat with asylum seekers under
OL,17,Fthe slogan "Scotland is at breaking
OL,18,Fpoint".
OL,26,@yD@LOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
