PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1776287489
OL,3,CLabour proposal to work with Reform in
OL,4,CScotland a 'lie', Scottish leader says
OL,6,FBut the SNP has been briefing for some
OL,7,Ftime now that there may be a "grubby
OL,8,Fdeal" struck up by Reform and Labour
OL,9,Fbehind the scenes.
OL,11,FIn Scotland, the voting system means
OL,12,Fthat a party with a minority number of
OL,13,Fseats may still be able to form a
OL,14,Fgovernment with the support of another
OL,15,Fparty. In this case, if the pro-union
OL,16,Fparties were able to set aside their
OL,17,Fdifferences then they may have been
OL,18,Fable to take the power away from the
OL,19,FSNP who have been in power in Scotland
OL,20,Ffor the past 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
